Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:51.80,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling to their coins squeezing out their wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:58.30,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels planning disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:05.31,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling on to their very last coins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.27,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Destruction and regeneration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:11.52,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You are the real enemy
